versions.description: Initial spec: scalar types, primaryKey, constraints, annotations
Collection types (list, map, stringSet, numberSet), nameOverride
Identity rebrand (primaryKey -> identity), enum supports (string|number)[], store-agnostic type descriptions
entityName PascalCase validation, field name reserved-word check, nested-field enum type matching, nullable property, binary type
Bare number/numberSet default changed from Double to Integer, schemaVersion tooltip clarified as customer-owned
